OL,5,G1000 Nightmare Tenants, Slum Landlords
OL,6,     FAfter moving abroad for work, a
OL,7,     Flandlord discovers that his
OL,8,     Ftenants have left him over 20,000
OL,9,     Fpounds behind with his mortgage.
OL,10,G1101 Traffic Cops
OL,11,     FAction-packed highlights from the
OL,12,     Fdocumentary series following
OL,13,     FYorkshire-based law enforcers. Can
OL,14,     Fthe cops stop a nighttime riot
OL,15,     Ffrom breaking out in Bradford?
OL,16,G1200 Traffic Cops
OL,17,     FIn Bradford there's a high-octane
OL,18,     Fchase through a housing estate,
OL,19,     Fand Yorkshire's back roads have
OL,20,     Ftheir peace disturbed by two cars
OL,21,     Fcarrying gun-toting drug dealers.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
